Package com.gemalto.mfs.mwsdk.provisioning.listener

Interface ReplenishmentPrepListener

public interface ReplenishmentPrepListener
This class is the callback during replenishment preparation time with MPA MPA will implement this class.
See Also:
ReplenishmentPrepStatus, ReplenishmentPrepStatus, SDKError
